<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Always invisible</strong> = Activate to make the variation invisible in the item list of the online store. When the option is activated, the variation can only be opened using the direct URL to the variation. The variation is not shown in the categories, search results or item lists, i.e. store specials, cross-selling and last seen items.<br></p>
