<p><strong>Do not administer stock for this variation</strong> = If this setting is selected, then the variation’s <strong>Stock</strong> tab will not include the sub-tabs <strong>Correction</strong>, <strong>Stock</strong>, <strong>Supply</strong> and <strong>Item movement</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div></div></td>
